des: This skill will read you facts that sound like they're true, but are, in fact, entirely made up. Whether it's something to surprise and astonish your friends, give yourself a laugh, or break up the monotony of a long day-whatever the reason, fake fun facts is here for you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
